  .col-md-4(style="margin-bottom: 2em")
    a(href='http://i.imgur.com/kHJVX.jpg')
      img.pluginImg(src='./assets/img/pluginicons/citadel.png')
      h3 Citadel
    p.
      Citadel is our protection plugin, designed to allow you to protect your buildings, doors, and chests from aggressors. It is built on the principle that protection requires resources, so to protect a block you must use any one of 3 resources: Smooth Stone, Iron, or Diamond. The more value the resource, the stronger the reinforcement.
    h4: a(href='https://github.com/erocs/Citadel') <i class="fa fa-github"></i> Github

  .col-md-4(style="margin-bottom: 2em")
    a(href='http://i.imgur.com/t9DaPOS.png') 
      img.pluginImg(src='./assets/img/pluginicons/jukealert.png')
      h3 JukeAlert
    p.
      JukeAlert lets players use jukeboxes (usually called 'snitches') to track and record the actions of other players in a small radius from the snitch. JukeAlert is integrated with Citadelâ€™s <a href='http://www.reddit.com/r/Civcraft/comments/y1rkd/citadel_20_commands/'>group system</a>
    h4: a(href='https://github.com/erocs/JukeAlert/') <i class="fa fa-github"></i> Github

  .col-md-4(style="margin-bottom: 2em")
    a(href='http://i.imgur.com/XbhkK.jpg') 
      img.pluginImg(src='./assets/img/pluginicons/prisonpearl.png')
      h3 PrisonPearl
    p.
      PrisonPearl allows players to restrain other players (see <a href='http://i.imgur.com/XbhkK.jpg'>this infographic</a> for the basics). Keep in mind that every day you have a player pearled consumes 2 coal from the chest, if there is not enough coal the prisoners will be freed. Also PrisonPearl is integrated with CombatTag, logging out will not save you from being pearled.
    h4: a(href='https://github.com/erocs/PrisonPearl') <i class="fa fa-github"></i> Github
