  .col-md-4(style="margin-bottom: 2em")
    a(href='https://github.com/gmlaxfanatic/FactoryMod/wiki') 
      img.pluginImg(src='./assets/img/pluginicons/factorymod.png')
      h3 FactoryMod
    p.
      Factorymod is a complex tech tree with the goal of allowing more efficient production from resources.. It transfers of all XP generation over to crop growing. You will not gain XP from killing mobs or mining normally. <a href='https://github.com/gmlaxfanatic/FactoryMod/wiki '>FactoryMod Wiki</a>
    h4: a(href='https://github.com/gmlaxfanatic/FactoryMod') <i class="fa fa-github"></i> Github

  .col-md-4(style="margin-bottom: 2em")
