    h4: a(href='https://github.com/Namrufus/RealisticBiomes') <i class="fa fa-github"></i> Github

  .col-md-4(style="margin-bottom: 2em")
    a(href='https://github.com/gmlaxfanatic/ItemExchange') 
      img.pluginImg(src='./assets/img/pluginicons/itemexchange.png')
      h3 ItemExchange
    p.
      ItemExchange allows players to set up chests and dispensers as shops. It is used in conjunction with Citadel to lock the container that is being used this way. Any item can be set up to be traded for any item. A single shop can offer multiple exchanges, for customers to choose between. <a  href='http://pastebin.com/raw.php?i=YrpYkjMa'>There's a guide here</a>
    h4: a(href='https://github.com/gmlaxfanatic/ItemExchange') <i class="fa fa-github"></i> Github
